						"description": "### Sign Up as a Vendor\n\nThis endpoint allows you to sign up as a vendor by providing the necessary information.\n\n**Request Body**\n\n- `username` (string): The username for the account.\n    \n- `email` (string): The email address for the account.\n    \n- `password` (string): The password for the account.\n    \n- `confirmPassword` (string): The confirmation of the password.\n    \n- `fullName` (string): The full name of the user.\n    \n- `phoneNumber` (string): The phone number of the user.\n    \n- `bio` (string): A brief bio or description of the user.\n    \n- `birthday` (string): The birthday of the user.\n    \n\n**Response**\n\n- `token` (string): The authentication token.\n    \n- `user` (object):\n    \n    - `username` (string): The username of the user.\n        \n    - `email` (string): The email address of the user.\n        \n    - `fullName` (string): The full name of the user.\n        \n    - `phoneNumber` (string): The phone number of the user.\n        \n    - `roles` (array): The roles assigned to the user.\n        \n    - `status` (string): The status of the user account.\n        \n    - `profileImageUrl` (string): The URL of the user's profile image.\n        \n    - `bio` (string): The bio or description of the user.\n        \n    - `id` (integer): The unique identifier of the user.\n        \n    - `birthday` (string): The birthday of the user.\n        \n\n**Example Response**\n\n``` json\n{\n    \"token\": \"\",\n    \"user\": {\n        \"username\": \"\",\n        \"email\": \"\",\n        \"fullName\": \"\",\n        \"phoneNumber\": \"\",\n        \"roles\": [\"\"],\n        \"status\": \"\",\n        \"profileImageUrl\": null,\n        \"bio\": \"\",\n        \"id\": 0,\n        \"birthday\": \"\"\n    }\n}\n\n ```"
					},
